{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Dit is het project waar ik aan gewerkt heb gedurende mijn stage bij een maritieme IT startup <a href=\"https://teqplay.nl/\">Teqplay</a>. Het doel van de applicatie was om zoveel mogelijk data van schepen te verzamelen uit verschillende bronnen, te combineren tot één master database en vevolgens in kaart te brengen waar alle data vandaan komt. </p>\n<p>Dus als iemand de vraag heeft over een schip: What happened? ShipHappens heeft het antwoord!</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7b366596cc03099d17a6d4edac2f7376/67148/shiphappens_1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 55.28846153846154%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Home Page ShipHappens\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/7b366596cc03099d17a6d4edac2f7376/dbb61/shiphappens_1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7b366596cc03099d17a6d4edac2f7376/19bd1/shiphappens_1.png 163w,\n/static/7b366596cc03099d17a6d4edac2f7376/d3bcb/shiphappens_1.png 325w,\n/static/7b366596cc03099d17a6d4edac2f7376/dbb61/shiphappens_1.png 650w,\n/static/7b366596cc03099d17a6d4edac2f7376/6b691/shiphappens_1.png 975w,\n/static/7b366596cc03099d17a6d4edac2f7376/67148/shiphappens_1.png 1248w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/92a7a9fb1013ba09580a7b438b1cd51f/c1e1e/shiphappens-search.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 59.240759240759246%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Zoek een ship\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/92a7a9fb1013ba09580a7b438b1cd51f/dbb61/shiphappens-search.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/92a7a9fb1013ba09580a7b438b1cd51f/19bd1/shiphappens-search.png 163w,\n/static/92a7a9fb1013ba09580a7b438b1cd51f/d3bcb/shiphappens-search.png 325w,\n/static/92a7a9fb1013ba09580a7b438b1cd51f/dbb61/shiphappens-search.png 650w,\n/static/92a7a9fb1013ba09580a7b438b1cd51f/6b691/shiphappens-search.png 975w,\n/static/92a7a9fb1013ba09580a7b438b1cd51f/c1e1e/shiphappens-search.png 1001w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9df3a50e529955b635ab4fabc24afad6/1842b/shiphappens-detailpage.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 47.794928335170894%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Details from ship\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/9df3a50e529955b635ab4fabc24afad6/dbb61/shiphappens-detailpage.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9df3a50e529955b635ab4fabc24afad6/19bd1/shiphappens-detailpage.png 163w,\n/static/9df3a50e529955b635ab4fabc24afad6/d3bcb/shiphappens-detailpage.png 325w,\n/static/9df3a50e529955b635ab4fabc24afad6/dbb61/shiphappens-detailpage.png 650w,\n/static/9df3a50e529955b635ab4fabc24afad6/6b691/shiphappens-detailpage.png 975w,\n/static/9df3a50e529955b635ab4fabc24afad6/91670/shiphappens-detailpage.png 1300w,\n/static/9df3a50e529955b635ab4fabc24afad6/1842b/shiphappens-detailpage.png 1814w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e78ea67bf382707681b54ed63d04e26d/6683a/shiphappens_master_table.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 47.32984293193718%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"master database\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/e78ea67bf382707681b54ed63d04e26d/dbb61/shiphappens_master_table.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e78ea67bf382707681b54ed63d04e26d/19bd1/shiphappens_master_table.png 163w,\n/static/e78ea67bf382707681b54ed63d04e26d/d3bcb/shiphappens_master_table.png 325w,\n/static/e78ea67bf382707681b54ed63d04e26d/dbb61/shiphappens_master_table.png 650w,\n/static/e78ea67bf382707681b54ed63d04e26d/6b691/shiphappens_master_table.png 975w,\n/static/e78ea67bf382707681b54ed63d04e26d/91670/shiphappens_master_table.png 1300w,\n/static/e78ea67bf382707681b54ed63d04e26d/6683a/shiphappens_master_table.png 1910w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h1>Tech</h1>\n<p>Het systeem is geschreven in Kotlin en de front-end is gemaakt met React, er wordt data binnengehaald van de Teqplay API, een CSV file, een XML file en userinput.\n<a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4e8c9e958bdfc3a3b56fd01f71cbec3e/ca9ca/component-overview-shiphappens.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 90.71161048689137%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"diagram shiphappens\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/4e8c9e958bdfc3a3b56fd01f71cbec3e/dbb61/component-overview-shiphappens.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4e8c9e958bdfc3a3b56fd01f71cbec3e/19bd1/component-overview-shiphappens.png 163w,\n/static/4e8c9e958bdfc3a3b56fd01f71cbec3e/d3bcb/component-overview-shiphappens.png 325w,\n/static/4e8c9e958bdfc3a3b56fd01f71cbec3e/dbb61/component-overview-shiphappens.png 650w,\n/static/4e8c9e958bdfc3a3b56fd01f71cbec3e/6b691/component-overview-shiphappens.png 975w,\n/static/4e8c9e958bdfc3a3b56fd01f71cbec3e/91670/component-overview-shiphappens.png 1300w,\n/static/4e8c9e958bdfc3a3b56fd01f71cbec3e/ca9ca/component-overview-shiphappens.png 1335w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"What happened? ShipHappens!","date":"2019-01-25","category":"projects"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/What-happened-shiphappens/"}}